Why nametags that show special cosmetics are bannable

By seeing someone's cosmetics that they are not wearing/you have not originally seen them wear, you are getting access to their inventory data, which qualifies as "unauthorized data access."

Most studios (alongside Another Axiom) treat that as reverse engineering or data scraping. (Section 8 point m. of Gorilla Tag's ToS gorillatagvr.com/tos)

